      • sendPayloadToSapAnywhere

        public static final void sendPayloadToSapAnywhere(AnwInventoryCountingPostDto payload)
                                           throws java.lang.Exception
        Method, which will send payload of inventory counting to the SAP Anywhere. Algorithm of sending inventory counting to the SAP Anywhere is simple:
        • post payload
        • get id, which was associated to the posted payload
        • close posted inventory counting
        Parameters:
        payload - - payload which represents inventory counting
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - possible exception during the processing
